From a44f144e6f8773c5f6d673853e0e6f0cc69b051d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 31 Jul 2025 01:08:45 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDP:CP:ath12k:wifi: Parsing of peer confing

Add changes parse NL command containing peer configuration details.
Extract each peer's MAC address, airtime value, group ID, and configuration
status bit. Store the airtime and group ID.

Add changes to send peer WMI command with the data received
through NL vendor command.

Patch-dependency: 0417-001-QSDK-CP-WMI-changes-for-ATF.patch
		  0417-002-QSDK-CP-NL-vendor-changes-for-ATF-offload.patch 
Patch-work: None

Signed-off-by: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
